        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-08-27 14:18:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nAndreas: firstly thanks for your approve.\nI am sorry that I cannot find out more suitable way to resolve this trouble in a short time.\n\nHonestly, the per-target based dt_sync() should handle all the low layer async updates in spite of whether it is via OSP async logs or not. Unfortunately, under current framework, it is not easy to do. Maybe we should make further work against LU-3469 patch (that was proved by Alex). We can discuss that with Alex after his vacation.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
